---
title: Sweet Chilli Chicken & Corn Veggie Toss with Asian Mayo & Spring Onion
description: A rich sauce can give a wealth of flavour to tender chicken breast. Take this soy sauce and mayo combination, it’s loaded with delicious aromas that elevate this sweet chilli chicken to the next level. For a pop of gold in your veggie toss add some charred corn to the mix. We’re sure your dinner experience will be newly enriched.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

*We’ve replaced the crispy shallots in this recipe with spring onion due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just
as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
